name: Listened to Program battle: Miami vs. Florida

content.html:
Florida Gators beat writer G. Allan Taylor joins Manny to discuss the recruiting battles being fought by Miami coach Mario Cristobal and UF coach Billy Napier — which have all been won by the Canes to this point. The discussion carries into the start of fall camp, realignment and how Miami could fit into the SEC, and where the Canes and Gators could be when they play each other next in 2024.
